Nairobi woman representative Esther Passaris has partnered KTN’s sister Radio station, Radio Maisha, and have been visiting children's homes and cheering them up this festive season. They have been distributing christmas gifts. Speaking at the rescue dada children's home in Pangani, Passaris has urged Kenya power and Nairobi water companies not bill such homes, calling it a disservice. There's a drop off point at the kick where well?wishers can drop off their donations